flowchart TD
    subgraph MH05_REFUND["MH-05: Refund Flow"]
        R1{Refund trigger?}
        R1 -->|Practice cancelled by master| R2[Auto full refund]
        R1 -->|User cancels more than 24h before| R3[Auto full refund]
        R1 -->|User cancels less than 24h before| R4[No refund, policy shown]
        R1 -->|Manual by admin| R5[Admin initiates refund]
        
        R2 --> R6[Payment Service calls Stripe refund API]
        R3 --> R6
        R5 --> R6
        R6 --> R7[Stripe processes refund]
        R7 --> R8[Webhook: refund.created]
        R8 --> R9[Update payment status]
        R9 --> R10[Notify user: Refund processed]
    end
